{"tid":1492583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察於記者會上形容未被審判之被捕人士為「犯人」","createTime":"2019-08-21T01:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T10:29:59.000Z","uid":127638,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d66c09a0d5152ded64850b70a676ca53b6652e24","tid":1492583,"uid":127638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:44:21.000Z","msg":"&lt;舊post開錯台，重post&gt;<br />\n<br />\n利申，無睇4點記者會，只睇視點31中剪輯記者會內容（隔離post）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8WyTnirXtXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8WyTnirXtXA&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41MbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=1ba96a1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8WyTnirXtXA</a> <br />\n<br />\n香港三權合一左？警察拉左人可以即判人入罪，稱被捕人士為「犯人」？咁係咪等於香港已經因爲警方而正式無左法治？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記者可唔可以幫忙質詢？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n事件令我諗起古裝劇審緊案都被稱為「犯婦人」！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發達如香港既地方點解法治會淪落到同古代中國有聯想？<br />\n真係好可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d628f6f5f3dd33b9eba848ead775075ecfd44751","tid":1492583,"uid":271234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:49:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"69c2edc706ed99eff1c6a41d6c4fbde9f34c3c5d","tid":1492583,"uid":127638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:33:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47cca39ac320afbeea09032dc8eb34968a44c8c6","tid":1492583,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:53:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48cbb7ca6733a67ee91092f841f34e1d831fee10","tid":1492583,"uid":127638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit